name: Emma Stone
description:
Emma Stone

Gorgeous actress, been in lots of great films (Easy A is still her best). I really like how lifelike this iteration turned out. Works well with all of the top models, esp. the photorealistic ones.

Nothing complicated here:

  • 2 vectors

  • 3e-03 rate

  • v1.4 base model

  • 7500 steps

  • .205 vector strength

Simple, yet effective :)

Do you like my work? Buy me a beer!
